<item>
            <title>[SPR-8766] Impossible to set SimpleMappingExceptionResolver.statusCodes</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8766</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bean property &apos;statusCodes&apos; is not writable or has an invalid setter method. Does the parameter type of the setter match the return type of the getter?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;indeed :&lt;br/&gt;
public void setStatusCodes(Properties statusCodes)&lt;br/&gt;
Map&amp;lt;String, Integer&amp;gt; getStatusCodes()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Probably a regression due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8452&quot; title=&quot;Expose statusCodes field in SimpleMappingExceptionResolver as a read-only map.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-8452&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-8452&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Works with 3.1.0.M2. Maybe works on jdk7 as Introspector was modified.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Why not make statusCodes a Map instead of Properties?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
